{"tid":1001691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發 支那製口罩含有致癌物","createTime":"2019-01-30T10:45:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T16:05:13.000Z","uid":32511,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d28c7ccaf3e7937d16e006a5185a4380959d4c97","tid":1001691,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T10:45:57.000Z","msg":"抗空汙戴口罩小心反傷身！據行政院消保處調查，市售標榜防霾、抗PM2.5口罩高達近7成品質不合格，其中，中國製口罩不但幾乎全不合格，更可怕的是甚至含有致癌物。<br />\n <br />\n綜合媒體報導，消保處調查市售口罩不合格比例高達68％，更有3成業者根本無法證明能有效抗空汙，品項包括中國廠牌SUN MILLION、Kootex、COCORO、振馨、QDY七朵雲與Honeywell，以及日本nepia與台灣易利用。<br />\n <br />\n消保官王德明特別點名中國製口罩維康與QDY七朵雲，更添加過量偶氮色料，有致癌風險。消保處提醒消費者，選購防霾口罩應留意有無通過國家標準檢驗，並仔細閱讀商品標示內容，若遇消費糾紛可向各地方政府申訴。"},{"pid":"99cf7af1eebe4648de1cd7970f8b531d4d93e9d4","tid":1001691,"uid":511,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T10:47:03.000Z","msg":"戴又死唔戴又死<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"383f5baa3993fee25f7228f2d6347e44d4fa68ab","tid":1001691,"uid":41974,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T10:48:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 防毒面具有毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ee9fba0fc36a5401b34849b5b742ed0d85fe752","tid":1001691,"uid":2383,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T10:48:33.000Z","msg":"支那真係地球癌細胞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b4203edf392caaf435afc7889ef748b4031a8b3","tid":1001691,"uid":156936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T10:49:13.000Z","msg":"住北京日日帶個班官仲唔嚇死"},{"pid":"58a01c2980fce7e011e84533ad8d67f564bb56c5","tid":1001691,"uid":9728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T10:50:57.000Z","msg":"諗唔明點解可以整親乜鳩都有致癌物"},{"pid":"a0e91c67986ec9924ca5d4327917c66ee2e97a92","